  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Enterprise
    Representation of the Enterprise, handles internal state for the Enterprise in our game.
    Entity
    Entity is used to represent an Entity or 'thing' for want of a better term in the Game.
    Galaxy
    Handles the Quadrants held within the Galaxy.
    Game
    The main Game class responsible for holding all relevant classes for the game coordinating player and enemy actions.
    Klingon
    Klingon handles Entity behaviour plus some extra behaviour including: processing an attack, handling the details of being hit, managing its own energy reserve.
    Quadrant
    Quadrant are sections of space with a randomised mixture of Stars, Klingons and Starbases.
    Star
    Star is a Entity that starts already scanned as it is pretty hard to not detect a Star in a Quadrant.
    Starbase
    Starbase is a Hittable Entity that can heal the Enterprise when it is adjacent to the Starbase in the same Quadrant.
    Stat
    Stat wraps a numerical int value, with a minimum and maximum value enforced inclusively.
    XyPair
    Represents a data object with an x and y Integer, used for things like position and vectors.
